3. cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) - The paper models the problem within a network flow framework, which is a topic in networking and internet architecture. 
4. cs.CE (Computational Engineering, Finance, and Science) - The paper proposes a computationally-efficient routing and rebalancing algorithm for the autonomous vehicles, which can be considered as a topic in computational engineering. 
5. cs.IT (Information Theory) - The paper deals with the problem of congestion-aware coordination of autonomous vehicles, which can be considered as a topic in information theory.
